{"tid":1398934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬，罷工都唔敢，你哋注定失敗","createTime":"2019-08-03T03:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:04:58.000Z","uid":58335,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2905d9e70b026ff422e49f052f633ef0594490","tid":1398934,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:54:08.000Z","msg":"搞幾多集會同散步都冇用<br />\n你班和理非用罷工已經係最好既支持<br />\n<br />\n如果你連呢樣又唔敢個樣又話有包袱<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁你到時唔好再問點解香港變成咁？<br />\n係你哋選擇左用自由民主換你份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a4ce8514b73d7e1b105b8d44f3b0590d36a9d64b","tid":1398934,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7874f10528cf62db40223f7796a9975a8ea9e33e","tid":1398934,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b765bf2b8669f6715f2a7af808ffe27f8bf3de8b","tid":1398934,"uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會交通塞車返唔到工呀??"},{"pid":"62b4fb2e8bac24f7e614c007fd45f286ffb8e0d0","tid":1398934,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"同我推上去<br />\n<br />\n「輿論戰」 【都市擂台】對於有市民發起的「不合作運動」，你支持嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/f83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fpoll%2Ff83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDdTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=c6e3645e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/f83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98</a><br />\n<br />\nbetween Chrome 無痕模式 可重複投"},{"pid":"09e005215c1dd8257021992920c993492f4ab513","tid":1398934,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"af9180d640373b4b58c2933df9935999a47857fe","tid":1398934,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49f874b7c46d726723b8d78d33ee23c605a279b","tid":1398934,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a060224a10e8edadab8dec5f1c227e7fdb780e9","tid":1398934,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"faffd4788d498b6a91574b4e58ff2a4b4d4f5c09","tid":1398934,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zoUBVt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zoUBVt.png&h=fac09fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d46d706c6e39654ccc0378c45dbede965a4321","tid":1398934,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876d7e3059c26b5d30d3756414578e5e0d0fe80c","tid":1398934,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5a27ed05cf257cf37f3521c06021fc059ea6ef","tid":1398934,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大大力推</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">衝衝子今日升哂級 和理非你唔係唔爭下氣啊？！？！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif